To run the demo:

$ export ICE_CONFIG=config

Or use --Ice.Config=config for all subsequent commands.

Start the IcePack service:

$ ../../../bin/icepacknode --Ice.Config=config --warn

In a separate window:

$ ../../../bin/icepackadmin -e 'application add "application.xml"'
$ ./client

This will deploy the servers described in the "application.xml"
descriptor and start the client.

Messages should be displayed in the IcePack service window.
